title: Andhaa Kanoon
subTitle: When his parents are killed by three men, Amar, Akbar and Anthony, Vijay teams up with a forest officer who was framed in a murder case to avenge their deaths.

title: Bacho Ke Sakha Bhagwan
subTitle: Children venture out on a pilgrimage and visit several holy shrines devoted to different gods, so that they can please them and ask for their help.

title: Khoj
subTitle: Ravi and Anita's vacation turns into a nightmare when Anita vanishes without a trace. Ravi's frantic search leads to more questions than answers when a woman appears, claiming to be his missing wife.

title: Muqadama
subTitle: Ajit returns home to see that his wife has killed herself after being raped by three men. He tries to avenge her but is caught by the police and sentenced to be hanged after he kills one culprit.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Singh Is Kinng
subTitle: Happy, notoriously famous for his antics, is sent to fetch Lakhan so that he can meet his ailing father. But, in Australia, Happy ends up taking Lakhan's place as the king of the local underworld.

title: Chatrapathi
subTitle: Separated from his family during a conflict, a refugee embarks on a mission to reunite with his adoptive family. However, he faces several challenges after his foster brother conspires against him.

title: Mr. & Mrs. Khiladi
subTitle: When stars misalign, love blossoms between an astrology-obsessed idler and a headstrong fish heiress whose father will settle for nothing less than a hardworking son-in-law.

title: Prem Granth
subTitle: Somen, a rich man, falls in love with Kajri, a village belle. However, they get separated when she suddenly leaves for unknown reasons.

title: Aadmi

title: Badal
subTitle: Badal's family dies at the hands of a corrupt police officer. While he is raised by his father's friend, he turns into a terrorist and vows to avenge his family's death.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.

title: Maa Ki Mamta
subTitle: Thakur Dharam seeks a nurse for his son after his wife passes away; the wife of one of his farm laborers agrees to help him.

subTitle: Thakur Dharam seeks a nurse for his son after his wife passes away; the wife of one of his farm laborers agrees to help him.

title: Vardaan Devi Maa Ka
subTitle: Tarigonda Vengamamba, an 18th-century poetess, devotes her life serving Lord Venkateshwara. She starts writing numerous songs for him and also considers him as her husband.

title: Naanu Matthu Gunda
subTitle: Shankar, an autorickshaw driver, adopts an abandoned dog and names it Gunda. However, his life turns upside down when his affection for the canine deepens.

title: International Khiladi
subTitle: An international crime boss and his journalist girlfriend fall victim to an elaborate conspiracy that claims an innocent life and turns them into bitter enemies.

title: Sirf Tum
subTitle: Deepak and Aarti fall in love with each other without ever meeting each other. Later, Aarti sets out to look for him in the city of Delhi.

subTitle: After graduating from a university in India, an unemployed man decides to try his luck in New York and gets caught in a love triangle between an equally unlucky girl and a rich girl.

title: Khiladi 786

title: Saugandh
subTitle: Sarang, an evil landlord, kills Ganga's family. Years later, Shiva, Ganga's son, marries Chand, Sarang's daughter, to seek revenge from Sarang by destroying his ego.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Zafar's obsessive love for Salma leads to her separation from her son, Iqbal. Twenty years later, Iqbal strives to reunite with his mother.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Zafar's obsessive love for Salma leads to her separation from her son, Iqbal. Twenty years later, Iqbal strives to reunite with his mother.

title: Kabzaa
subTitle: Ravi works for Veljibhai Soda, a gangster, and does illegal work for him. Once, he is asked to vacate Ali from his property, but he gets inspired by his ideals and decides to change his ways.

title: Fateh
subTitle: Ranvir, Karan and Salim, commandos trained by Major Anand, are shattered when the latter is killed. They soon learn that a gangster, Samrat, may be responsible for his death and try to find the truth.

title: Heropanti 2
subTitle: A vigilante is sent on a mission by the government to kill enemy troops. However, things go wrong when he's mistaken for the leader of the troops.

title: Double Dhamaal
subTitle: Four idlers make elaborate plans to earn money by investing in buildings but are conned by Kabir, who leaves them unemployed and penniless. Soon, they are on the prowl to avenge their humiliation.

title: Surya The Soldier
subTitle: When a soldier lands in trouble due to his anger issues, he begins seeing a psychologist in hopes of one day returning to duty.

title: Koi ... Mil Gaya
subTitle: A young man with special needs is influenced by his father's scientific work. He encounters an alien who grants him extraordinary abilities and transforms his life.

title: Rudrangi
subTitle: Bheem Rao Deshmukh, a tyrant who oppresses his people, is drawn to a beautiful woman named Rudrangi and desires physical contact with her. In order to satisfy his obsession, he terrorises her village.

title: Laadla
subTitle: Raju, an upright union leader, can do anything at his wheelchair-bound mother's behest, even if it means breaking his own heart and giving in to a rude heiress.

title: Kudrat Ka Kanoon
subTitle: When the good doctor Vijay is falsely accused and imprisoned, his wife and daughter, desperately seeking justice, are terrorised and slandered by the harsh eyes of the society.
